.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, green, ivory, yellow, blue
The people have 5 different jobs:  nurse, paramedic, firefighter, librarian, project-manager
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: orchid, daffodil, lily, aconite, azalea
House: palace, modern, cape-cod, craftsman, tower
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, helicopter, van, quad-bike, ship

1. the nurse is the person who likes red
2. the paramedic is the person driving the airplane
3. the palace house is the person who likes green
4. the firefighter is the modern house
5. the person who likes green is to the right of the person who likes ivory
6. the person who growsorchid is the person driving the ship
7. the person who growsdaffodil is the person who likes yellow
8. the cape-cod house is in the middle
9. the librarian is on the far left
10. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter
11. the person who growsdaffodil is to the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike
12. the person who growsaconite is the craftsman house
13. the project-manager is the person who growsazalea
14. the librarian is to the left or right of the person who likes blue

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Job	|   librarian	|    firefighter	|     nurse	|    paramedic	|    project-manager	|
| Color		|    yellow	|      blue	|      red	|     ivory	|     green	|
| House	|     tower	|      modern	|      cape-cod	| craftsman	|     palace	|
| Flower		|     daffodil	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| aconite	|   parliament	|
| Transport		|     helicopter	|     quad-bike	|     ship	|     airplane	|     van	|
